{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c642ea380b","title":"关于确定中央政治局扩大会议开会地点的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7efab77005","index":0,"year":1960,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"c642ea380b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji43","name":"毛泽东全集第43卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/43-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji43":{"comments":[{"id":"872bbe49ca","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这次会议后来于1960年1月7日至17日在上海举行。"},{"id":"931f7417ee","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柯庆施，当时任中共中央政治局委员、上海市委第一书记。江渭清，当时任中共中央候补委员、江苏省委第一书记。"},{"id":"100fc30168","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"富春，即李富春，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记。"},{"id":"175cf518eb","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"江华，当时任中共中央候补委员、浙江省委第一书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b23ff37fae","type":"title","text":"关于确定中央政治局扩大会议开会地点“的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b"},{"id":"872bbe49ca","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇、小平同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b"},{"id":"931f7417ee","type":"paragraph","text":"柯庆施、江渭清二位同志不赞成在南京开会，他们考虑到有几种不甚妥善的因素，主张在上海开。富春同志有信给我，赞成村等意见，要我向中央建议改变地点。江华同志从上海开会回来，又口头向我转达了此意。请你们召集常委谈一次，考虑一下，是否可以改变地点，并用电话向村等询问南京所以不宜开会的详细理由，是否有安全原因和房屋原因。再则是否也可以考虑另一地点，即广州，那里有温暖的好处，但时间要推退三天到五天，因为一律要坐火车去，不能坐飞机。以上请的处","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b"},{"id":"100fc30168","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b"},{"id":"175cf518eb","type":"paragraph","text":"一月一日上午五时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b"}],"page":{"id":"31a6d3c05b","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"c642ea380b","start":106,"end":106}}}},"__N_SSG":true}